==English==

===Noun===
'''celestial sphere'''
# {{astronomy}} An [[abstract]] [[sphere]] of [[infinite]] [[radius]] which serves as the imaginary [[backdrop]] for [[celestial]] objects, and of which the visible sky is one [[hemisphere]].

====Synonyms====
*[[empyrean]]
*[[firmament]]
*[[heavens]]
*[[vault of heaven]]
*[[welkin]]

